                            <comment id="14737054" author="githubbot" created="Wed, 9 Sep 2015 15:39:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user fhueske commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1112#issuecomment-138950226&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1112#issuecomment-138950226&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

